msgstr "龙炎剑"

msgid "desc_r_Dragonfire"
msgstr "火在这把剑里永远燃烧着,这把剑最初是由Yssam的龙王Far-Loradan的崇拜者使用的."

msgid "r_Dwarven Greatsword"
msgstr "矮人巨剑"

msgid "desc_r_Dwarven Greatsword"
msgstr "Dvergheim官僚风格的齿轮符号装饰着矮人巨剑矮小的十字型护手."

msgid "r_Dwarven Zweihander"
msgstr "矮人双手剑"

msgid "desc_r_Dwarven Zweihander"
msgstr "这把矮人之刃是根据Dvergheim的第一位国王所使用的原版剑打造的."

msgid "r_Ember Falchion"
msgstr "宝石偃月刀"

msgid "desc_r_Ember Falchion"
